1) What does REPL stand for?

Correct

Correct answer
Read Evaluate Print Loop

Explanation
REPL stands for "Read Evaluate Print Loop". This means that each line is calculated and the result is printed to the screen before putting the user back at a prompt.

Further Reading
https://linuxacademy.com/cp/courses/lesson/course/1486/lesson/1/module/158

